      <span class="font-bold text-baits-blue">SME Working Capital Loan</span> is a loan scheme supported by EnterpriseSG and granted to the borrower (a business entity) through the Participating Financial Institutions (PFIs). The loan, capped at S$1M, is repayable on equal monthly instalments over the approved loan tenor, capped at 5 years, depending on the approving financial institutions. The current risk sharing is 90% between EnterpriseSG and the PFIs.
